{"tid":1988594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日媒稱金正恩手術失敗後變植物人","createTime":"2020-04-25T10:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T11:56:32.000Z","uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"19fa1583946357e245422f376cc11b63bec7a9df","tid":1988594,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:08:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522696-20200425.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522696-20200425.htm&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=36c9836d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522696-20200425.htm&h=9fd1f32e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522696-20200425.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5608964e843b353b1fb339b661ed4747221a3731","tid":1988594,"uid":93649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:08:45.000Z","msg":"是但啦"},{"pid":"85268b574095fd4c141976d4301c9d773536102b","tid":1988594,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:08:47.000Z","msg":"日本傳媒報道，日前傳出病危的北韓領袖金正恩變成植物人。<br />\n<br />\n日本《週刊現代》報道，金正恩日前進行「心臟支架手術」失敗後，變成植物人。北韓其後要求中方派出醫療團隊協助，路透社報道，中共中央對外聯絡部一名高級官員，星期四率領包括醫療專家的團隊從北京前往北韓。<br />\n<br />\n今日是北韓人民革命軍建軍88周年，官方朝中社詳細介紹軍隊成立的歷史，未有提到金正恩公開活動的消息。《勞動新聞》在社論中強調了金正恩呼籲加強軍事力量，敦促進一步強化全軍對他領導的支持。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普早前表示，金正恩病危的報道不正確；南韓外交部亦多次指出，未收到平壤政府有異常動靜。<br />\n<br />\n路透社早前引述南韓一名消息人士稱，金正恩仍然在生，可能很快會露面。"},{"pid":"efc2c4b2379fa57ebfff0e04722ccb19c1ab3606","tid":1988594,"uid":154255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:17:40.000Z","msg":"屌你幾十個post都講撚緊啦<br />\n發現新大陸咩"},{"pid":"7fc89024566a4e188579bf0521da2cecdc9a2e14","tid":1988594,"uid":221171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T11:56:32.000Z","msg":"出埋啲垃圾po洗太平地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0sefaGC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0sefaGC.jpg&h=d20263cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A7KOvGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA7KOvGE.jpg&h=d79ae067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OtSo31F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOtSo31F.png&h=98f62511&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}